FBIS3-11836 "drlat059_p_94001" FBIS-LAT-94-059 Document Type:Daily Report 25 Mar 1994 Ecuador Government Switches Support to Gaviria for OAS Post PA2503173194 Madrid EFE in Spanish 1704 GMT 25 Mar 94 PA2503173194 Madrid EFE Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] Quito, 25 Mar (EFE) -- The Government of Ecuador announced today that it will vote for Colombian President Cesar Gaviria for OAS secretary general, and not for Costa Rican Foreign Minister Bernd Niehaus, whom it had promised earlier to support. The announcement of the vote change at the OAS is included in a brief, two-paragraph communique issued this morning by the Foreign Ministry.
